Class ThreadContextMapFilter

    @Plugin(name="ThreadContextMapFilter",
        category="Core",
        elementType="filter",
        printObject=true)
 @PluginAliases(value="ContextMapFilter")
public class ThreadContextMapFilter
extends MapFilter
    Filter based on a value in the Thread Context Map (MDC).
